Welcome to this issue of Power Online's (http://www.poweronline.com) 
electronic
newsletter brought to you by VerticalNet. We've got some big shows coming up
for the power generation industry. Texas A&M University Turbomachinery
Laboratory is sponsoring the 29th Turbomachinery Symposium Sept. 18-21 at the
George R. Brown Convention Center in Houston. For registration info, check out
the story in Power Online's Latest Headlines, and don't forget to visit the
lab's new Power Online Storefront. All kinds of shows are scheduled for
October, including Powersystems World 2000, Oct. 1-5, in Boston. For more info
on that show and others, check out Power Online's Events Calendar (under
Resources on the home page). Until next time, take care. ACM


