******** 3M SOLUTIONS *********

In response to customer requests, 3M has introduced a web-based version of
its popular 3M Service Life Software. This software offers an easy method for
estimating the service life of 3M gas and vapor respirator cartridges--for 
many
organic as well as some inorganic contaminants.  See
http://www.poweronline.com/ecommcenters/3m.html for more details.


