1) Book Selection -- Simulation of Industrial Processes for Control Engineers
Author: Philip J. Thomas
Computer simulation is the key to comprehending and controlling the full-scale
industrial plant used in the chemical, oil, gas and electrical power
industries.  Shows how to use the laws of physics and chemistry to produce the
equations to simulate dynamically all the most important unit operations found
in process and power plant.
